high_descs: Move to the coffee table in front of the couch.
Pick up a credit card from the table.
Move to the dining table behind you.
Place the card on a plate on the table.
Pick up the plate from the table
Move to the shelf to the right of the coffee table under the TV
Place the plate on the shelf.
anns.task_desc: Put a plate with a credit card on the shelf in front of the couch.

high_descs: Turn right, head to the wall, turn right, head down to the round table in the middle and face the computer on the table.
Pick up the blue credit card on the table.
Turn around, bring the card to the dining table.
Put the card on the plate on the table.
Pick up the plate with card from on the table.
Turn around, head to the round table, turn right to face the white shelf along the wall.
Place the plate with card on the shelf.
anns.task_desc: Put a card on plate, on a shelf.

high_descs: Turn left, then go straight, then turn right, then go straight, then turn right, and turn to face the coffee table.
Pick up the credit card from the coffee table.
Turn around, and go straight to the table.
Put the credit card on the plate, on the table.
Pick up the plate from the table.
Turn left, then turn left, then go straight, then turn left to face the counter.
Place the plate on the center of the counter.
anns.task_desc: Put a plate with a credit card on the counter.

high_descs: Turn to your right and walk across the room, then turn right again until you reach the end of the black, round table.
Pick up the credit card on the bottom tier of the table.
Turn around and walk to the white, table behind you.
Place the credit card on the plate that is in front of the newspaper.
Pick up the plate with the credit card on it.
Turn around and walk forward until you reach the round, black table, then turn right and walk up the the TV mounted on the wall.
Place the plate with the credit card on it on the ledge beneath the TV.
anns.task_desc: Put a plate containing a credit card on the surface under the TV.

high_descs: Turn right, move to the low part of the coffee table.
Pick the credit card up from the low part of the coffee table.
Turn right, move to the dining table, behind the plate.
Place the credit card on the plate.
Pick up the plate with the credit card on it.
Turn left, move to the shelf in front of the TV.
Place the plate onto the shelf below the TV.
anns.task_desc: Place a credit card below the TV.
